channel.description:
Rob Trudell's Adventure, Discovery and Exploration of his surroundings with a push to map it out and learn about it with those who wish to join.  

Events, Places and People contrasted from mundane to exciting to purposely compose a video library that shares information with a community of eyes to build further in both depth and breadth.

He strives to overcome Barriers, both real and imagined and attempts to understand and uncover myths in enjoyable ways.
channel.title: Robert Trudell
